column1: Baby Barnaby's////So we get there on a Sunday and of course there's a crazy wait. There should be. This place is legit. So when we're finally called in I've already decided what I'm getting: Green eggs. Scrambled eggs with spinach
column3: and jack cheese? Hell yeah. Sign me up for seconds! My best friend sitting with us tells me to get the biscuits instead of the bagel. Listen to me when I say this. Get. The. Biscuit. The meal also came with this amazingly delicious and mouth watering apple chicken something sausage. HOLY HELL. YES. Breakfast potatoes were also legit.
